53.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-34\" data-attachment-id=\"658104\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06055316/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-34.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-34/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06055316/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-34-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152808/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-411-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-41\" data-attachment-id=\"658196\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152808/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-411.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-41-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152808/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-411-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152658/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-331-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-33\" data-attachment-id=\"658188\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152658/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-331.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-33-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152658/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-331-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c