3.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-10\" data-attachment-id=\"658165\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152350/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-101.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-10-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152350/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-101-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152834/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits1-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits\" data-attachment-id=\"658199\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152834/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits1.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-44/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152834/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits1-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152218/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-310.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152218/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-310-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-3\" data-attachment-id=\"658158\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152218/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-310.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-3-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152218/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-310-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBack to the matter at hand – and no, I’m not being blinded by my rose-tinted glasses here – DTM was a victim of its own success. With every year, the competition pushed teams to pour more and more money into their cars, and by 1992, the Group A era had come to an end. The next three years of technical warfare between teams ultimately led to less exciting racing as the cars became more complex and fragile as a result.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152318/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-61.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152318/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-61-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-6\" data-attachment-id=\"658161\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152318/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-61.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-6-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152318/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-61-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152501/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-191-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-19\" data-attachment-id=\"658174\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152501/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-191.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-19-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152501/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-191-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152326/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-71-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-7\" data-attachment-id=\"658162\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152326/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-71.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-7-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152326/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-71-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eActive aero, weight transfer systems, sequential gearboxes, electronic diffs in four-wheel-drive systems, and traction control – by the time the 1990s rolled around, the rawness was gone. DTM was effectively absorbed into the ‘International Touring Car’ series by 1996, and by 1997, the Deutsche Tourenwagen Meisterschaft was effectively dead. While the German Super-Tourenwagen series tried to pick up where the DTM left off, it wasn’t until 2000 that German touring cars were back in force.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152436/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-161.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152436/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-161-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-16\" data-attachment-id=\"658171\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152436/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-161.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-16-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152436/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-161-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152200/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-210-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-2\" data-attachment-id=\"658157\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152200/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-210.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-2-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152200/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-210-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152344/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-91-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-9\" data-attachment-id=\"658164\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152344/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-91.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-9-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152344/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-91-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152334/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-81-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-8\" data-attachment-id=\"658163\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152334/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-81.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-8-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152334/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-81-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eMercedes-Benz, Opel, and Audi (via ABT) introduced a new breed of V8 coupés based on the CLK, Astra Coupé prototype, and TT silhouettes, respectively. While initially successful, over the next 20 years, DTM regulations would find varying degrees of success and complexity before succumbing to GT3-based regulations to keep – you guessed it – ever-rising costs in check.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06055245/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-27.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06055245/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-27-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-27\" data-attachment-id=\"658097\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06055245/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-27.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-27/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06055245/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-27-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eToday, the racing is fantastic, but so is GT3 racing around the world. DTM isn’t alone in losing its unique character, and it points to a deeper problem: how technical advances have drained the rawness from motorsport – and, in many ways, enjoyment in our everyday lives.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152300/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-44.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152300/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-44-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-4\" data-attachment-id=\"658159\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152300/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-44.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-4-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152300/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-44-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152358/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-111-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-11\" data-attachment-id=\"658166\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152358/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-111.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-dtm-edits-11-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152358/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-111-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152405/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-121-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH DTM Edits-12\" data-attachment-id=\"658167\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/09152405/EMS-24-MC-SH-DTM-Edits-121.jpg\" data-can-